commit.title: Make Opaque/Transparent/Strategy import-time instead of require-time
commit.message:
Make Opaque/Transparent/Strategy import-time instead of require-time

In the ring plugin infrastructure, the [Strategy expand [PEeval].] in
the various foo_polynom files needs to be restated the corresponding
foo_tac file (foo_tac is the one that's imported whenever we want to
make the ring tactics available, usually by exporting it in a more
general file like Ring.v).
